works.description:
These apps are just WebViews which point 

to our website (http://freeandroidtv.com/). Normally, I'd be fine with the
 
free traffic, but I already have a "Watch TV" app which points to the  
website on Google Play  
(https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.watchtv) and these apps
 
detract from my downloads. Secondly, these apps include very intrusive  
notification ads, so I get complaints to my website because of them.
